metadata.name: Audrey
metadata.description:
Audrey is a Bombshell, with her vixen vibes and razor sharp wit. She's got the ability to attract men, even when she doesn't want them. Her pin-up style always steals our hearts.

If you love the vintage look, our Audrey Pin Up from the Bombshell Collection is for you. The neutral colors make it work in any room of your house.
